{"id":"79b42d7e4c8e80d7ce53a8e4921eca2fba05107a4eda640e7ed9e19a5c979288","item_id":"73a4816fd3:0","text":"此节点允许使用 mask 进行纹理分层。这适合向纹理结果中添加贴花、标签、损伤等效果。"}
{"id":"8eefb77c10b9a9978163980904e89e3106717fb08c4ee935b1f0ea309fdc1fba","item_id":"73a4816fd3:1","text":"与所有纹理类节点一样，此节点接受一个 manifold，用来描述应用纹理的 2D 或 3D domain。如果未连接 manifold，默认行为是在几何体上定义的 s,t domain 上应用纹理，这通常称为 \"UV Layout\"。"}
{"id":"a1e724ab5ef0190cb86935fd2d862983150ac1f34c67041e7b267573ef11d63e","item_id":"73a4816fd3:2","text":"提供对纹理文件的访问。Texture atlas format（纹理图集格式）文件可以按 UDIM (Mari)、ZBrush 或 Mudbox 格式读取。此 plugin 也支持 Rtx procedural texture plugins。"}
{"id":"8dd6857baf02685094c2585a53d1f1fb4806c188f3a303eba245cd16e917f840","item_id":"73a4816fd3:3","text":"Mute"}
{"id":"df7a355454275952f064dd21a6788d8275fac4315a50410c51084892253e440f","item_id":"73a4816fd3:4","text":"在合成链中忽略此节点。"}
{"id":"6cb3fdd092ff8a9b50499e636d77bea14eed33318c6172378bfb3cd0eaa50500","item_id":"73a4816fd3:5","text":"Texture Overlay"}
{"id":"afe64286fef40d74ec96dd03466561c0940689ede4e8a72100a325c6889d31c1","item_id":"73a4816fd3:6","text":"可在此连接一个 overlay（叠加）输入，从而串联多个 texture nodes。"}
{"id":"4beb4ed5d53eadc9d3dc0c28ab16285edbf9fd98555277fd8c783384903f2c86","item_id":"73a4816fd3:8","text":"Mask Value"}
{"id":"2faed1c7855188904fb3b09d03eb26cab3f8d32d119ee3d853aec617d352bfbc","item_id":"73a4816fd3:9","text":"用于控制此纹理在合成链中可见性的标量值、pattern 连接或另一个灰度纹理。建议在下面的参数中使用 Texture connections（纹理连接）。"}
{"id":"76ad11f725e867ae6237a19ae291eaf6cc3b7044026ff32b8f1c31ce496cfba7","item_id":"73a4816fd3:10","text":"Mask Texture"}
{"id":"e12a3aae53bccb590aaafde71359706876ae9dfa3dcadec55cedb961fb1d622e","item_id":"73a4816fd3:11","text":"用于控制此节点可见性的 RGB 纹理。"}
{"id":"b61dddb16cfc3188429adbb61484c7d3496280ed3a48f533f49fd172d0b57752","item_id":"73a4816fd3:12","text":"Mask Channel"}
{"id":"03600b692562de97cf534fe4ffdef1f603e135118e57067933e6aab3fe71eefa","item_id":"73a4816fd3:13","text":"从上面的纹理输入中选择 mask channel 的 channel offset。"}
{"id":"a5a0585fe7e00edb7eb0c8de0ab5c0ecfdd2fdaee57e357fba331a921f160b0d","item_id":"73a4816fd3:14","text":"Mask Atlas Style"}
{"id":"34dd2a1755670a5d767c4ee7fd2e13ebafb607a497296c8ef07174d73a8511b4","item_id":"73a4816fd3:43","text":"如果指定 atlas style，则"}
{"id":"f974a07ea4988c92d27cf645c46bc533075d4dd5a8059c03fe460a4aa9d4dd5a","item_id":"73a4816fd3:44","text":"filename"}
{"id":"61d2ad82ae72aa75864e82e41522b354f533a00ba370a05231a5b05acaf1d127","item_id":"73a4816fd3:45","text":"必须包含 _MAPID_；它会根据 surface parameterization 和"}
{"id":"088f5c2cf37f54e03a01979895bad1aac4dda32dffbb4c509abd47738fecb8a1","item_id":"73a4816fd3:46","text":"atlasStyle"}
{"id":"b0b9bc302cc09c8b4b39970a6a2e178c45dd65e14830b5be7881b434259f22db","item_id":"73a4816fd3:47","text":"自动替换。对于第一个 UV tile，Mari UDIM 示例会是 Diffuse1001.tex，其中 \"1001\" 会替换纹理 filename 中的 _MAPID_。"}
{"id":"8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e","item_id":"73a4816fd3:48","text":"Value"}
{"id":"34403a6de5b95efb588d3d3840eeab3f04e7e55b3449fec3ec3ed337a411cf04","item_id":"73a4816fd3:49","text":"Application Style"}
{"id":"1dbe4d3a655d8919ac8c71583d4ab6426cb2b6c7b3b22b6ee6bcdfc889cbe8ab","item_id":"73a4816fd3:50","text":"Example (Diffuse_MAPID_.tex)"}
{"id":"dc937b59892604f5a86ac96936cd7ff09e25f18ae6b758e8014a24c7fa039e91","item_id":"73a4816fd3:51","text":"None"}
{"id":"367f137ed5a73cd9244364f9b856e152825c7ee7b2bbadc11f5db692603f1a16","item_id":"73a4816fd3:52","text":"UDIM (Mari)"}
{"id":"787c8d1749b89ff31d6dfd3cc486228a57d0ce6c9eab7826d5b3d4118ac55637","item_id":"73a4816fd3:53","text":"Diffuse1001.tex, Diffuse1002.tex, etc."}
{"id":"3fd9fa12c4e59043ab799b5a8939b960875f08684dd28e88755850acb1a9a2c8","item_id":"73a4816fd3:54","text":"UV Tile Base-1 (Mudbox)"}
{"id":"43c03f208f71e02626e206abb6f21c88b5703b11637566bfa8313468eb9c92b7","item_id":"73a4816fd3:55","text":"Diffuse_u1_v1.tex, Diffuse_u1_v2.tex, etc."}
{"id":"e0a64989813515caaff0da7d497e5df53efe949e226766974c008d060cbd1ccd","item_id":"73a4816fd3:56","text":"UV Tile Base-0 (ZBrush)"}
{"id":"690a001a95c4c37625f530507ed23b46245ce53fafd2bed69fda6b7cbcc63c07","item_id":"73a4816fd3:57","text":"Diffuse_u0_v0.tex, Diffuse_u0_v1.tex, etc."}
{"id":"7e2e0cf23bbdf0eefc9713338af6d24b4bcfe67530cb4249a2d4bd2b9c8c77db","item_id":"73a4816fd3:30","text":"Missing Mask"}
{"id":"77f4c5a0e4ce108dd69cdecd66f46a08fa571286aaadd6306e38309b94980d22","item_id":"73a4816fd3:31","text":"当以上某个连接或参数无法读取或使用时，使用此 value 或 pattern 输入。这是一个有用的 fallback。"}
{"id":"63b2e7266d46f9d68d60ef374f6abcc6d90bebb7947d53217d625d8b2b0a45e5","item_id":"73a4816fd3:32","text":"Texture Input Parameters"}
{"id":"971b974235a86ca628dcc713d6e2e8d975206cc84c858720ce046c2dab72855a","item_id":"73a4816fd3:33","text":"Filename"}
{"id":"203132c560e342be3d3c0c9480b3d6a8755017cf7dcce62fca132e2ac4d17248","item_id":"73a4816fd3:34","text":"纹理的 filename。必须提供此参数。"}
{"id":"4e8c6a6f5453e4ee04c20beb5d095921c9a3cefbe16decebbdb75070f4a21c22","item_id":"73a4816fd3:35","text":"要使用图像序列，通常会通过字符串替换构造纹理贴图引用，在你偏好的表示方式中嵌入帧号。示例如下："}
{"id":"a1410ecb239c26bbb53ced673056418dd99c3032e6474613ed3fcdc73fc9324d","item_id":"73a4816fd3:36","text":"(Maya)   $PROJPATH/sourceimages/flapping.<f4>.tex"}
{"id":"c9b390054a9f72b30c258f67a3dd8de455ff3847ce77ea1e7cae5bc23b5b1d24","item_id":"73a4816fd3:37","text":"(Katana) '/images/flapping.%04d.tex' % frame"}
{"id":"f6a83fd956f58207cd76f35178e14abca26a1a2c8056ba2237601bc19d3a05d3","item_id":"73a4816fd3:38","text":"(Houdini) 在文件名中使用 $F、$F3 或 Houdini expressions：`padzero(3, $F)`"}
{"id":"fd6352db603160ce0757d37804323f31695ee925f4e532eb2cd29b83585389a0","item_id":"73a4816fd3:39","text":"最好避免在文件路径中使用特殊字符、变音符号和空格，因为它们可能无法正确解析，导致纹理渲染失败。"}
{"id":"f006aa17de7681cdae37fe9fccbdbb515dbb50f4b25cb2828479c84f9e96b858","item_id":"73a4816fd3:40","text":"First Channel Offset"}
{"id":"144900f46bb6ac21222425e4307695902bf786e34048b18bde9deed924b2ea35","item_id":"73a4816fd3:41","text":"Offsets（偏移）要查找的第一个 color channel。"}
{"id":"e5e1e2b3b2ea6e5e3e3294eb36b6d7ff4a7cc8fb79e891e166361284569defa7","item_id":"73a4816fd3:42","text":"Atlas Style"}
{"id":"e2b62a06cd950665b0c339619c5a7c3a559ae20f55af09dad7ff99ce17837ed1","item_id":"73a4816fd3:58","text":"在所有 atlas texture workflows 中，用户应避免使用负的纹理坐标"}
{"id":"e3109eb112b8b5d6dd25efb433f70bf813e165da8c7f3800a0e999d7ee918b11","item_id":"73a4816fd3:59","text":"Invert T"}
{"id":"e9cdc66df02e2065430cd72b8873eddf88edd30e4f8590e7bb2696c79b1a8563","item_id":"73a4816fd3:60","text":"反转用于纹理查找的 t 参数。"}
{"id":"fd515a1e5b893197b489340b7b320167bd55936624b0c197f7901fc497364847","item_id":"73a4816fd3:62","text":"提供应用纹理的 domain。默认使用 s,t。可在此提供一个 manifold 来调整纹理放置，例如："}
{"id":"6b34a2c213ce84c498a12614eb533686f9ffebb9fb047c08753afdf5c88f2406","item_id":"73a4816fd3:63","text":"PxrManifold2D"}
{"id":"794ee7c012118f94dcfe7c44ac2ead73efaf47e4e19c566159b9c2d4cb4445e5","item_id":"73a4816fd3:64","text":"Texture Filtering（纹理过滤）"}
{"id":"22a1383aa9e7630e6eee982fb703a7bf128560ef1464a85e2d43de82e1aefb43","item_id":"73a4816fd3:66","text":"选择可在纹理查找期间使用的不同重建过滤器。PxrTexture 可用的过滤器包括："}
{"id":"feb761df94a0f71d286844666fdc012fb2dbf67d5cf1df0b367d92189fe7399e","item_id":"73a4816fd3:67","text":"0: Nearest"}
{"id":"9b1263f8a10d901dc14a393ce4440ace399fffa6323153a10125a94fdecd0994","item_id":"73a4816fd3:68","text":"1: Box"}
{"id":"c5645a6021411eaaac581410f17bea2f01c36b99cab5181421529a8080dee5a0","item_id":"73a4816fd3:69","text":"2: Bilinear"}
{"id":"8c4028c0340c0b2e7039572340b2405845aa3fc1b6c6c9188389ec118eef7c3f","item_id":"73a4816fd3:70","text":"3: Bspline"}
{"id":"3a74d9fd200699afceee46892fadb65c63031320817d29f8425b373c38d00fd4","item_id":"73a4816fd3:71","text":"6: Gaussian"}
{"id":"9f146d1e365af9062b65e2c47a38f3e3ac175134c6deabd6f2bb13d82c96a27a","item_id":"73a4816fd3:72","text":"7: Lagrangian"}
{"id":"e7ec98f39ceb641cd216a2d40c0de606152ab5cf9469eaa4f2cd6d5a71e6f7a3","item_id":"73a4816fd3:74","text":"指定从纹理文件取回的图像要模糊多少。"}
{"id":"4809c0208c8ceeb9166a48f46aa04e6e4ca4298ddd7885afca7eeb986ab348da","item_id":"73a4816fd3:75","text":"Mip Interpolate"}
{"id":"befce626792d6ae4eedf09a5e5d846c50ba8147d80ce14f1ad0b3cffb79f445a","item_id":"73a4816fd3:76","text":"选择是否在多分辨率纹理的相邻分辨率之间插值，使层级之间的过渡更平滑。"}
{"id":"8205c2948d1174986c32262849ca9c80f36a830916aa75b33e25914fb466dce9","item_id":"73a4816fd3:77","text":"Missing Color"}
{"id":"616cf7e60fa24ba4356f391bf74b9b7b651f7a6715792b639191fe58eea78598","item_id":"73a4816fd3:78","text":"如果打开纹理时出错，则使用此颜色。"}
{"id":"7faa2a5bb19807b0f12cf84876e26b3247057ae8fdc3c2be6692013fac4ccc3c","item_id":"73a4816fd3:79","text":"Missing Alpha"}
{"id":"47d96edde546d8d86e1d1cecbf96052ff5620fd67f1d1001be0737e1c2750a2b","item_id":"73a4816fd3:80","text":"如果打开纹理时出错，则使用此 alpha。"}
{"id":"22d4f6088b718aa471d4b671e7497315ff13df122c585460169d106c713a20c2","item_id":"73a4816fd3:81","text":"Advanced Settings"}
{"id":"b8ec4a849a91caf29c71452ab560d3a0da6ffc253c64a3737680c58a42e25f6d","item_id":"73a4816fd3:82","text":"MipBias"}
{"id":"50e7ee32c6062625996f4c81a947615ae433bcc1c46fd2f63b9a7ccfbafff2f4","item_id":"73a4816fd3:83","text":"Bias（偏置）渲染时的 MIP 选择，可选择更高分辨率（负整数）或更低分辨率（正整数）。"}
{"id":"6960e01a00d0599446e00ff16d67c2dda5a8214709238c5b736828bf9540edca","item_id":"73a4816fd3:84","text":"MaxResolution"}
{"id":"17b3c4b7121231235ff66b6001d868b4b7fdcddc86a9d915e7c663b44cf86b80","item_id":"73a4816fd3:85","text":"Clamp（钳制）MIP 选择到首选最大 level。根据你的选择，这可能阻止最高分辨率参与渲染。"}
{"id":"6ef489404633ce65e77b99e79095e5abf2dad6cc62214755a38d919c7cb0df07","item_id":"73a4816fd3:86","text":"OptimizeIndirect"}
{"id":"58479a3adad995e2b71bc70dd67769e562e2c2da4f04bfc59d9415525301e17c","item_id":"73a4816fd3:87","text":"在 indirect hits 上将 texture filter 设置为 Box（开销较低），而不是使用为其他可见效果选择的 filter。"}
{"id":"17e3ebe8c64dfdca5029438edc630690f6bdcd4677c1393e001e2465ac25d241","item_id":"73a4816fd3:89","text":"Linearize"}
{"id":"5fdc9a4dbeff45ccce191b5c6ec8f168e3ed9be28ff97184f3f72e29347d3043","item_id":"73a4816fd3:90","text":"对纹理应用反向 sRGB transform。如果你在 sRGB space 中绘制纹理（大多数绘制软件包的默认设置），但在数据线性空间中查看数据，纹理会显得发白。此选项会将 sRGB transform 应用于纹理，使其再次呈现为视觉上线性。"}
{"id":"9f2d118c615b3f7f614fbfbcc4fd3edd5dfb4ce781bea7c19155ea8f53fe3a16","item_id":"73a4816fd3:91","text":"Color Tint"}
{"id":"357de7170a2a222705b18022e71d03f3ccfaa3e29f07d77afef37049ca7c6318","item_id":"73a4816fd3:92","text":"纹理中颜色值的 multiplier，可用于调整亮度或操控单个 color channel"}
{"id":"c54f3e0aa08775c55e47d2cf166b9abf18efa1edd69d16a07effb5ef590201d4","item_id":"73a4816fd3:93","text":"Color Offset"}
{"id":"53974a1945e8609215f7432f457ea84d46c68c98bfe25df5e3a212b92cef82f0","item_id":"73a4816fd3:94","text":"对结果应用 offset，使结果颜色发生偏移"}
{"id":"d2d41840b0bd8ed83165ea423add0d32a458a3131d16c1bb74727934d32d3633","item_id":"73a4816fd3:97","text":"经过过滤的颜色结果。注意，所有结果都会从"}
{"id":"0de71a697592df3ad7b5517a221898e7b95f7b06fc3e05be27a969c5980dcb67","item_id":"73a4816fd3:98","text":"startChannel"}
{"id":"b8a85fbf026e9eb3b371b9d91e7516a4e80c0e4913ed905e5ba42fe5f340e0d6","item_id":"73a4816fd3:99","text":"offset 开始查找。"}
{"id":"7ae85c2d0074f0b45ec3f98d2f40a5f79e86abedd6e35ab372b9d21772a2c28a","item_id":"73a4816fd3:101","text":"R channel 结果"}
{"id":"696353435479edc46a3e8ec45c217c084c9d249ddcb922a3445131f174d9c090","item_id":"73a4816fd3:103","text":"G channel 结果"}
{"id":"691964dd34e3c6e471f04289a508b02ddba69e7fd40aca1f59ebcba4d5401255","item_id":"73a4816fd3:105","text":"B channel 结果"}
{"id":"890f7aa1b6882bd3a2548401dd7ae638108b8010a3cbcc25974c005ba36f3048","item_id":"73a4816fd3:106","text":"resultA"}
{"id":"18881bf0cbd3b5d11609dd7b52a3c598fdddd4696d4686ca6d930d1765562262","item_id":"73a4816fd3:107","text":"如果 alpha 存在且 resultRGB 已连接，则返回 RGB 后面的 channel。如果 RGB 未连接，则返回第一个 channel。"}
{"id":"34dd2a1755670a5d767c4ee7fd2e13ebafb607a497296c8ef07174d73a8511b4","text":"如果指定 atlas style，则"}
{"id":"f974a07ea4988c92d27cf645c46bc533075d4dd5a8059c03fe460a4aa9d4dd5a","text":"filename"}
{"id":"61d2ad82ae72aa75864e82e41522b354f533a00ba370a05231a5b05acaf1d127","text":"必须包含 _MAPID_；它会根据 surface parameterization 和"}
{"id":"088f5c2cf37f54e03a01979895bad1aac4dda32dffbb4c509abd47738fecb8a1","text":"atlasStyle"}
{"id":"b0b9bc302cc09c8b4b39970a6a2e178c45dd65e14830b5be7881b434259f22db","text":"自动替换。对于第一个 UV tile，Mari UDIM 示例会是 Diffuse1001.tex，其中 \"1001\" 会替换纹理 filename 中的 _MAPID_。"}
{"id":"e0a64989813515caaff0da7d497e5df53efe949e226766974c008d060cbd1ccd","text":"UV Tile Base-0 (ZBrush)"}
{"id": "e368929abd3614e92ad17e56175b67d1f6ba94aca92ab43b7f16f31764ff7447", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:7", "text": "Mask"}
{"id": "e29793dea8429f58cc913ce697117a3614eaa231b5a3942af954b66c44d43850", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:61", "text": "Manifold"}
{"id": "638e249f4a15ebb84957da130701d138a6e06d88dceeaa2e6dcd91db70cc1381", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:65", "text": "Filter"}
{"id": "cd83e6731d2b17369af0704c1f52ff42262363a5521f650c36383b48bd35833b", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:73", "text": "Blur"}
{"id": "c4e5fedaa99fc544be5c72eb62e337e9682348aada0b8913ba713b2430f7d75d", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:88", "text": "Color Correct"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:95", "text": "Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:96", "text": "resultRGB"}
{"id": "c9223602a8320733dcf0de118c9880f9df06acdfdb068bb26ba166fc96c52d6c", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:100", "text": "resultR"}
{"id": "2e12f103dc4a4b216b21cc6f017371b08507fc67f2a1ad9f133aa333afe0fc11", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:102", "text": "resultG"}
{"id": "c3719f180d82ecafb70ce347c3499e7668a3d9262533cadae303c770922865ff", "item_id": "73a4816fd3:104", "text": "resultB"}
